      * Remaining Software tasks: RSV support, scalability testing, possible osg-configure changes, documentation
      * Remaining Release tasks: ITB and other external testing, documentation

   * *Hadoop Distributed Filesystem (HDFS) Version 2.0*
      * Major upgrade from the current OSG production version 0.20
      * Software team has completed build(s), done a fair amount of internal testing, and fixed many issues
